    <h4 class="page-header">Revolutionizing the Market</h4> 
    <p>Throughout our years of experience providing HPE quotations for customers, it became increasingly clear just how difficult it was to obtain a fast and accurate quote on a customized HPE server. This was a complaint expressed by many in this industry. The whole process was slow, frustrating and very outdated.</p> 
    <h4 class="page-header">Server Configuration</h4> <p>Our super-fast, one of a kind online configurator allows you configure your HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 server online, selecting from a huge range of configurable items to receive an immediate quote.</p> <p> Designed to be very easy to use, our industry leading online configurator features all HPE quick spec catalogues, allowing you to configure online and get instant prices.</p> <p> All orders are verified by our technical sales team, ensuring that your HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 Server is fully compatible. We have done the legwork so you don&rsquo;t have to, making the entire process a breeze.</p> 
    <h4 class="page-header">Powerful Processors</h4> <p>ServerWarehouse delivers totally customizable HPE ProLiant DL360 servers with a huge range of configuration options. This powerful, 1U rack server is configurable with Intel Xeon Scalable processors and offers both single processor and dual processor options.</p> <p> Intel Xeon Scalable processors are available in four ranges; Bronze, Silver, Gold and Platinum.<br> Bronze processors are perfect for small businesses, as they are built to perform best with basic storage servers. The Silver processors is optimized for developing IT organizations, providing the speed and security necessary for your data center. </p> <p> Intel Xeon Gold processors deliver high level reliability, hardware-enhanced security and the high performance ideal for high intensity, demanding workloads. Intel Xeon Platinum processors provide what is quite possibly the very best performance in this industry for mission critical, AI, machine learning, cloud workloads and real time analytics. They also provide huge leaps in I/O, storage, memory and network technologies.</p> 
    <h4 class="page-header">Features</h4> <p>Intelligently designed, easily manageable and surprisingly expandable, the ProLiant DL360 Gen10 is a superb choice for businesses that require a lot of power.</p> <p> The HPE&rsquo;s ProLiant DL360 Gen10 manages to fit a huge range of features into a slim-line 1U chassis due to its well-thought out internal design. In addition to its support for Intel&rsquo;s core-heavy Xeon Scalable processors, it has experienced a significant internal redesign which has allowed it to offer a significant choice of storage options. It features 24 DIMM slots and memory capacity of a huge 3TB.</p> <p> A powerful server, which is well suited to rack dense applications that require significant processing horsepower. As the whole Xeon Scalable processor family is supported, the system can be customized for almost any workload. </p> 
    <h4 class="page-header">Models</h4> 
    <div class="row"> <div class="col-lg-6"> <strong>HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 - 8 Bay SFF 8x 2.5</strong> <p>The HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 – 8 Bay SFF 8x 2.5&rdquo; utilizes hot-swap 2.5&rdquo; drives for denser storage capabilities. 2.5&rdquo; drives are more power efficient than their 3.5&rdquo; counterparts. </p> <p> This model supports dual processors and is powered by the 2nd Gen Intel Xeon Scalable family. It features 2x PCI Expansion slots and supports up to 24 modules of registered 2933Mhz DIMMs (RDIMMs) memory. </p> <strong>HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 - 4 Bay LFF 4x 3.5</strong> <p>The HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 – 4 Bay SFF 8x 3.5&rdquo; supports 3.5&rdquo; drives, which offer certain advantages over 2.5&rdquo; drives. These include generally possessing higher capacity and being more cost-effective. </p> <p> The HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 – 4 Bay SFF 8x 3.5&rdquo; is a dual processor system powered by the 2nd Gen Intel Xeon Scalable processor family. It features 2x PCI Expansion slots and supports up to 24 modules of Registered 2933Mhz DIMMs (RDIMMs) Memory.</p> </div><div class="col-lg-6"> <strong>HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 - 10 Bay SFF 10x 2.5&rdquo; NVME/SAS/SATA Drive</strong> <p>The HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 – 10 Bay SFF 10x 2.5&rdquo; NVME/SAS/SATA, is a dual processor system powered by the Intel Xeon Scalable processor family. It supports up to 24 modules of Registered 2933Mhz DIMMs (RDIMMs) Memory and features 2x PCI Expansion slots.</p> <p> This model supports 2.5&rdquo; NVMe/SATA/SAS hard drives. Each storage protocol features their own unique advantages, the HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10 – 10 Bay SFF 10x 2.5&rdquo; NVME/SAS/SATA supports them all, giving you the choice to configure with the storage type that best fits your needs. </p> </div> </div> <h4 class="page-header">Vigorously Tested HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10</h4> <p>ServerWarehouse servers are fully and comprehensively tested by our experienced engineers, who are on hand to answer all your queries and offer whatever advice you may need. Your customized HPE server will arrive pre-built and fully tested.  </p> <p> With over 3 decades in this field, we have served some of the largest organizations on the planet. These include the likes of the BBC, NASA, Virgin, Disney, CERN, Sony, Google, the University of Oxford, Sky, Rolls-Royce and Toshiba. </p> 
